Introduction

ZZBest (Korean: 지지베스트; Japanese: サポートベスト) was an 5-member girl group under Faith Entertainment. They consisted of: Dana, Hanb, Miri, Ina and Dayoung. The group debuted on January 15, 2015. They are assumed to have disbanded in November-December 2015 without any official statement.
